wBAY">doi</a>:<a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="//doi.org/10.17645%2Fpag.v6i1.1186" id="mwBAc">10.17645/pag.v6i1.1186</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Politics+and+Governance&amp;rft.atitle=Democracy+and+Human+Rights%3A+Concepts%2C+Measures%2C+and+Relationships&amp;rft.volume=6&amp;rft.issue=1&amp;rft.pages=48&amp;rft.date=2018&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.17645%2Fpag.v6i1.1186&amp;rft.aulast=Landman&amp;rft.aufirst=Todd&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ADemocracy" class="Z3988" about="#mwt23" id="mwBAg"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt23" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwBAk"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-7" id="cite_note-7"><a href="./Democracy#cite_ref-7" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-7" class="mw-reference-text">Wilson, N.G. (2006). <i id="mwBAo">Encyclopedia of ancient Greece</i>. New York: Routledge. p. 511. <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt27" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"ISBN","href":"./Template:ISBN"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"0-415-97334-1"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBAs"/><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" about="#mwt27" id="mwBAw">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" about="#mwt27" id="mwBA0"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/0-415-97334-1" title="Special:BookSources/0-415-97334-1" about="#mwt27" id="mwBA4">0-415-97334-1</a>.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-8" id="cite_note-8"><a href="./Democracy#cite_ref-8" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </